page.title: 13BOYS BRIGADE
page.content: BB stands for Boys Brigade .It is held on a Tuesday night.It is held at the Methodist Church.You get badges and play games.Last week Pinderfields Hospital Health Centre came.I got a certificate for doing life saving.We did it on a dummy.We sometimes go swimming,on a Friday night,at Silcoates school.Last week it finished at 9:15.I have got a white badge,a green badge and a purple badge.There is a tuck shop.It is 25p subs.There is a camp and when we go it will be my birthday.I am taking a birthday cake.We need a ruck sack and a pen knife.We are going camping to the moors.The Boys Brigade have a sports day every year.
